Given the previous setup and the additional requirements for user login functionality, handling invalid login attempts, and session timeout, I will expand on the existing folder structure.

## Updated Folder Structure:
my_project/
├── backend/
│   ├── models/
│   │   ├── user_model.py
│   ├── views/
